articles.title: Index rises as Omicron fears subside - Philstar.com
articles.description: Stocks in the Philippines and most Asian bourses edged higher yesterday, cruising in the slipstream of another record-setting day on Wall Street, as traders shrugged off the worst fears of the impact of the Omicron variant and returned to risk assets.
